        This class provides the proper structure for Envelope Defaults to be used to inject (pre-fill) data into a Template

        Parameters:
        recipientDefaults - The defaults object for Recipient data. Optional.
        emailSubject - The subject of the email sent to the signer(s). Optional.
        emailBlurb - The message in the body of the email sent to the signer(s). Optional.
        envelopeTitle - The title of the envelope. Optional.
        tabValueDefaults - Map of Tab value defaults, mapping tabLabel to the desired value. Value format will be validated according to Tab type. Optional.
        customFields - The custom fields to be associated with the Envelope. Optional IF the customFields on the account are not required.
